al clock time.\nThe corrected distance-redshift relation of cosmic observations due to the\ndistant clock effect are also discussed, which again gives a redshift\nindependent fraction $\\Omega_{de}=\\frac{2}{\\pi}$. The theory is consistent with\ncurrent cosmic observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Jan 2014 00:48:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Mar 2014 09:33:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 4 May 2015 01:19:04 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 16 Jun 2015 06:14:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
